{
  "name": "RPlog_Axel_and_Raver",
  "title": "Axel and Raver",
  "summary": "In a bar on a busy world, the cold-blooded pilot Axel Vichten takes exception to a man snoring atop a passed-out pilot and -- with a sly smirk -- draws his hand cannon and shoots the offender clean off him, scattering the room. The recruit Raver, also known as Ravaun Huckleberry, lies pinned and unmoving while his commanding officer, the Lieutenant Alex, and the bystander Cade watch the violence unfold; Cade had been asking Alex how his brother died flying with the War Shrikes. Axel tosses credits to clean up the mess and lectures the trapped recruit on competence, demanding he disarm before leaving, while Alex repeatedly orders the stubborn Raver to comply. The standoff escalates as Axel shoots Raver's holdout weapon from his arm and Alex finally bellows for everyone to stand down, calling med-evac. With Raver wounded and uncooperative, Alex forces a vial of medication into his mouth as he thrashes and threatens her, and Axel pointedly advises her not to tell her command what drug she just administered before the bloody encounter ends.",
